| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5152 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 04fd5ec4-ab25-5ad1-a3ee-54e2b1dc3408"
